---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy | A1 Service Expert"
  description="Cookie policy for A1 Service Expert website. Information about cookies we use and how to manage them."
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="prose prose-slate mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-brand-black">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: November 2025</p>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device when you visit a website. They help websites remember information about your visit, making your browsing experience more efficient and personalized.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        We use cookies on our website to:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>Understand how visitors use our website</li>
        <li>Improve website functionality and user experience</li>
        <li>Analyze traffic patterns and popular content</li>
        <li>Remember your preferences (where applicable)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

      <div class="mt-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-black">Essential Cookies</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
          These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly. They enable basic features like page navigation and access to secure areas.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-black">Examples:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>Session cookies (expire when you close your browser)</li>
            <li>Security cookies (to prevent fraud)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-black">Analytics Cookies (Google Analytics)</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
          We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our website. These cookies collect anonymous information including:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
          <li>Number of visitors and page views</li>
          <li>How long visitors stay on pages</li>
          <li>Which pages are most popular</li>
          <li>Traffic sources (e.g., search engines, direct links)</li>
          <li>Browser type and device information</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-700">
          This data is anonymized and helps us improve our website and services.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-black">Google Analytics Cookies:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li><strong>_ga:</strong> Distinguishes unique users (expires after 2 years)</li>
            <li><strong>_gid:</strong> Distinguishes unique users (expires after 24 hours)</li>
            <li><strong>_gat:</strong> Throttles request rate (expires after 1 minute)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Some cookies are placed by third-party services that appear on our pages:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Website analytics (privacy policy: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
        <li><strong>Google Maps:</strong> Location and directions (when embedded)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">5. Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        You can control and manage cookies in several ways:
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-brand-black">Browser Settings</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
        Most browsers allow you to:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>View cookies stored on your device</li>
        <li>Delete all or specific cookies</li>
        <li>Block all cookies</li>
        <li>Block third-party cookies only</li>
        <li>Clear cookies when you close your browser</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-3">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-brand-black">How to manage cookies in popular browsers:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings → Privacy and security → Cookies and other site data</li>
          <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Settings → Privacy & Security → Cookies and Site Data</li>
          <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences → Privacy → Manage Website Data</li>
          <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings → Privacy, search, and services → Cookies and site permissions</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-brand-black">Google Analytics Opt-Out</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
        You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking by:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>Installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a></li>
        <li>Blocking analytics cookies in your browser settings</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">6. Impact of Blocking Cookies</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Please note that blocking or deleting cookies may impact your experience:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>Some website features may not work properly</li>
        <li>Your preferences may not be remembered</li>
        <li>We won't be able to improve the website based on usage data</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-700">
        Essential cookies cannot be disabled as they are necessary for the website to function.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        We may update this cookie policy from time to time to reflect changes in technology or legal requirements. The latest version will always be available on this page with the revision date clearly indicated.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">8. More Information</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        For more information about cookies and how they work, visit:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li><a href="https://www.allaboutcookies.org" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">All About Cookies</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://ico.org.uk/for-organisations/guide-to-pecr/cookies-and-similar-technologies/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">ICO Guidance on Cookies</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-black">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-700">
        If you have questions about our use of cookies, please contact us:
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-base text-slate-700">
        <p><strong>A1 Service Expert</strong></p>
        <p>11 Cunliffe Dr, Kettering NN16 8LD</p>
        <p>Phone: <a href="tel:07394433889" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">07394 433889</a></p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@a1serviceexpert.com" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">support@a1serviceexpert.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
